[Dylan] Yeah.

05:00.633 --> 05:02.367
Which I can legally
do since I bought it.

05:02.367 --> 05:04.067
It's in my name, so...

05:05.633 --> 05:07.500
[Tom] Not here, could
it be under the bed?

05:07.567 --> 05:08.700
[Dylan] Might be.

05:11.267 --> 05:13.433
[Tom] No. Alright,
let's move this.

05:16.067 --> 05:17.433
Alright, what is this?

05:17.800 --> 05:19.067
This mean anything to ya?

05:19.067 --> 05:20.900
[Dylan] Rohypnol,
that's where they are.

05:20.900 --> 05:22.067
[Tom] What?

05:22.067 --> 05:23.300
He kept saying
someone stole 'em,

05:23.300 --> 05:25.400
But they've been sitting there.

05:25.400 --> 05:27.533
These are what he
OD'ed on in Rome.

05:27.533 --> 05:29.200
[Tom] Well she didn't
want us to take those.

05:29.200 --> 05:30.367
Yeah.

05:31.200 --> 05:33.067
[Tom] Uh, wait a minute.

05:33.067 --> 05:34.400
Would she be okay
if you keep 'em?

05:34.400 --> 05:35.500
[Dylan] Yeah.

05:41.800 --> 05:43.200
Are they legal here?

05:43.200 --> 05:45.067
[Dylan] Yeah, they're
completely legal, they're like...

05:45.067 --> 05:46.467
[Tom] What are they used for?

05:46.467 --> 05:47.900
[Dylan] They're
sold as a sedative for

05:47.900 --> 05:50.533
Sleeping ailments, and sometimes
they're given to people...

05:50.533 --> 05:51.900
[Tom] And if we get
pulled over, you're not

05:51.900 --> 05:53.767
Gonna get arrested
for havin' those?

05:53.767 --> 05:55.600
[Dylan] No, they're fine.

05:57.967 --> 06:00.700
Well it's obviously
not here, the shotgun.

06:00.700 --> 06:04.100
No, and I dunno
where it would be.

06:12.533 --> 06:13.233
[Tom] Is there anywhere else?

06:13.233 --> 06:14.267
[Dylan] No.

06:15.167 --> 06:16.333
[Tom] Okay.

